#### What is the expected behavior?
As user I want to select the content of a HTML element.

#### What is the current behavior?
When I use a matTooltip in a html container like div or span, the user can not select the content for copy/paste:
```<span matTooltip="Can't select text">A text to select, but can not select</span>```

#### What are the steps to reproduce?
https://angular-material2-issue-cef8r3.stackblitz.io
OR:
Just copy the code snippet from above into your HTML page....

